title: SSD Distribution shoud only be available to users verified with proofOfTwitter.
body: Only users verified with with proofoftwitter should be able to receive SSD distribution. I love the idea of anonymity but, the reality is, for a DAO to function the voting members must be real individuals. Otherwise, voting power can be rewarded unfairly.
author: 0x8237c3EB572DBc370cCe499a09F57c9986971e40
